content: Bharat Bandh from tomorrow: What is open and what is shut – check list here  The Financial ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: While the trade unions linked to the BJP and the TMC have not called for a strike, those belonging to the Congress and the Left parties have called for a two-day strike on March 28-29.
